Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:43.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だぁれ　一緒に遊ばな…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:13.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,日が暮れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:20.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,家に帰らなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:24.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここはどこ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:37.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,早く家に帰らなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:02.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やれやれ　日の暮れるのが早くなったな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:20.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当にこっちでいいんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:25.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,安心おしよ　大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうだか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だいたいばあさん　なんであんな所にいたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:37.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それがねぇ　どうしてだかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おーい　ばあさんやーい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:49.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ばあさん　みかげやーい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:52.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じいさんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:57.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おーい　陽吉さん　こっちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:07.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当に　なんとお礼を言えば良いか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,途中でとんでもないもの拾ったと思いましたがね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ご苦労かけましたな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,わしは少々足が悪いでな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんな奥までは　山に入れん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:25.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そなたが通らなかったらと思うと　ぞっとしますわい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:32.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大したお礼もできませんが　せめて休んでいってください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:33.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そりゃどうも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:39.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,しかし　なぜ山に入ったのか分からないでは心配ですな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:46.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれはこの頃　たまにこういう事がありましてな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:54.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,夕方になると　今日のような夕焼けの日なんかは特に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:58.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,帰ると言って　家を出ようとするのですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:06.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,年を取ると　稀にそう言い出す者がいるとは聞いた事があるが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:11.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,子供の頃の記憶に　一時的に戻ってしまうとか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:17.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その頃の家に　帰ろうとしているのかもしれませんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:22.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まぁ　わしもあやつも長く生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:25.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あちこちガタがくるのも当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:30.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また　そうやって人の事もうろく扱いして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:32.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当の事だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:37.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私ゃまだあんたよりよっぽど働きますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そっちこそ一人じゃ飯も炊けないくせして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私がいなくなったらどうすんのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何を偉そうに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もうろく言われたくなかったらしっかりしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お客の前で　でかい声出すんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どっちがだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんた　蟲師なのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,昔この里にもいたねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:07.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,娘の疳の蟲やらイネの病気やらで世話になったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:09.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうだったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これで膝が治るって？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:20.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そう言やなんか楽になったな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当かい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:37.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,明日の朝　もう一度すれば完治するはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつはありがたい　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,恩に着る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:01.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ギンコさんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ばあさんのことだがね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:17.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,年を取って　子供の頃の事を思い出すというのは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:21.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,昔の記憶を無くした者にもあるのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さぁ　そこまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ばあさん　記憶が無いのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:39.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれは昔　突如この里に現れたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:45.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,普段はもう　そんなことを忘れてしまっているのだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:51.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　ふと思い返すたび　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:07:00.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれは一体なんだったのだろうと　思うのだよ
