Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰だ　お前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:27.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,アカネは　それきり姿を消した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,名前は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,里はどこだい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと気味が悪いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ありゃ　鬼の子じゃあるまいか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあアカネちゃんは　鬼に食われちまったってのかい
