Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:03.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やがて　その子を引き取ると名乗り出たのは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,アカネの父だった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:15.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,考えてみりゃ　あの子もかわいそうなもんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,健気なもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの子　遊びにまざってこないね
