Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,当然のように思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:52.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,夕方になるたび　帰るなどと言い出すまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,妙な話だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:05.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ばあさんは　自分の故郷の事をいつか思い出すのかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:14.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうしたら　やはり帰りたいと思うのかのう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,夕暮れ時に　人が入れ替わる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それと同じ現象を聞いた事がある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:34.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,夕暮れ時にのみ現世に現れる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,「大禍時」というものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それにのまれた者は　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:46.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,夕暮れ時　本体の無い影のみの姿で現れる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:54.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そして　その影に踏まれたり踏んだりすると
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,影の本体と入れ替わりに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大禍時にのまれてしまう　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,…のだろうと考えられている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:10.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何せ　そうやって現れた者は そこまでの記憶が無くなっているため　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,実証は無い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:19.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　アカネはみかげと入れ違えに…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:26.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なら　アカネはその後　どうなったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあな　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:32.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　同じように誰かと入れ替わって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:35.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこかで暮らしているんじゃないだろうかね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:39.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこに現れたかは分からんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:45.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大禍時は現世とは別の所にあるという
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:48.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いつ　どこでつながるかは分からん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:13:01.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,アカネも　どこかで幸せになってくれてるといいが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:22.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう飽きちゃった　綾取りしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　影踏みの続きしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:45.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんた　誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:55.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いやぁ　お陰ですっかりよくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:56.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そりゃよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:01.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そういや　同じような足の悪い連中が数人いてな
