Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:43.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,膝から何か出たぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　楽になったな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うちのじいさんのも…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これはただの痣ですな
